headline: Is Smurfit Westrock (SW) Pricing Look Attractive After Mixed One Year Share Performance
summary: If you are trying to figure out whether Smurfit Westrock at around US$40.95 is a bargain or just fairly priced, this review is written for you. The stock has shown mixed recent returns, with about 5.4% over the last week, 13.6% over the last month, 3.4% year to date and an 18.3% decline over the past year. The 3 year and 5 year returns sit at 15.4% and 3.0% respectively. Recent coverage around Smurfit Westrock has focused on how investors are reassessing packaging and materials names, with...
